    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready to roll up your sleeves and bring this classic back to life! This vehicle is the perfect project for a dedicated DIYer or someone looking for a budget-friendly way to get into a new ride. While it\u2019s currently in poor condition and needs a fair amount of mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a complete restoration. Grab this opportunity to customize a car exactly how you want it at a price that leaves plenty of room for your upgrades!",
