      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This beauty is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and there isn't a single scratch or speck out of place. It drives like a cloud and looks even better in person. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I do! Come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
